  "title": "Warehouse Supervisor",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job scope:</strong><br /><br /><strong>Inventory & Stock Control</strong></p><ul><li>Manage the receipt, storage, and distribution of materials and components.</li><li>Ensure high inventory accuracy through routine cycle counts and annual physical audits.</li><li>Oversee the picking process to confirm all required parts are collected and prepared for production\nactivities.</li></ul><p><strong>Logistics & Distribution</strong></p><ul><li>Coordinate inbound and outbound shipments with internal teams and freight forwarders.</li><li>Verify all incoming goods against Purchase Orders and technical specifications.</li><li>Prepare and manage shipping documentation, including packing lists and export paperwork where required.</li></ul><p><strong>Operational Excellence</strong></p><ul><li>Improve warehouse layout to enhance picking efficiency and material flow.</li><li>Maintain a clean, well-organized warehouse in line with 5S standards.</li><li>Ensure all warehouse equipment, such as forklifts, racking, and weighing scales, is properly maintained and\ncertified.</li></ul><p><strong>Multinational corporation</strong></p><p><strong>5 days office hours</strong></p>",
